{"tid":333214,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"片長720小時 《Ambiance》2020年上畫一次即銷毀","createTime":"2017-07-23T15:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T04:50:35.000Z","uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db70bb3bdfaba8a250e30f6e4d4b5bb84ee9d135","tid":333214,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/07/20170723_wyc_246_13/gamersky_01origin_01_20177231581F3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F07%2F20170723_wyc_246_13%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_20177231581F3.jpg&h=b058d390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海報表示一段72分鐘的先導預告即將到來（不是完整預告）<br />\n<br />\n　　這部電影由瑞典導演Anders Weberg執導，入行已20年的他希望能在退休前完成《Ambiance》這部超長電影，並在2020年上畫。雖然目前暫不知本片講述的是甚麼主題和故事，但Weberg表示片中可能不會有一句台詞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n　　為了拍攝這部電影，Weberg每星期都要完成至少一小時的成片，而目前他剛完成了本片前400個小時內容的製作。此外Weberg還表示，《Ambiance》在全球只會上畫一次，之後他就會銷毀這部電影的所有備份，令其無法再登上大銀幕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/07/20170723_wyc_246_13/gamersky_02origin_03_201772315879D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F07%2F20170723_wyc_246_13%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_201772315879D.jpg&h=09b1c7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早在2014年，Weberg就發佈了《Ambiance》的預告片，長達7分鐘，而在2016年他發布了第二條預告，長達7個小時，不僅超過了所有的電影預告片長度，連大部分電影都甘拜下風。此外，Weberg還計劃在2018年發佈電影的正式版預告，長達72小時，並在之前發布一段72分鐘的先導預告&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇左條trailer 感覺creep creep地 我係凡人 唔係好知佢想表達d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLevgVmZ8rE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRLevgVmZ8rE&d=L%2FxfbXTRjRaY9sdF6SQAx%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e8570ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLevgVmZ8rE</a>"},{"pid":"75b2d80419c4de15ed7922a2c1162e4c43f59463","tid":333214,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"究竟咁樣仲算唔算電影"},{"pid":"d03a8ea54382ad927689960eb361d83d675c7c79","tid":333214,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"好似啲webcam scene<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a7e7841e4152aadf09fd750e874ad62ba818da","tid":333214,"uid":9767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"On9到 個導演一定以為自己好有創意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7043f795d846beafb89daf4fd656053458b8162","tid":333214,"uid":54988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"懶係有藝術咁 收皮啦佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ee69797aba112943de9a1833cd815fe06e0926","tid":333214,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%9D%E5%9C%8B_(1964%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B8%259D%25E5%259C%258B_%281964%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%29&d=L%2FxfbXTRjRaY9sdF6SQAx%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1eaec676\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%9D%E5%9C%8B_(1964%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1)</a><br />\n諗起呢套野"},{"pid":"f06573676215b0457c221ce9672a7d4941df38c2","tid":333214,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"睇一分鐘已經頂唔住，仲話720小時，痴根"},{"pid":"515e09895fc92773891d903a7f988d6e0d658949","tid":333214,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"我都可以做導演  放部機係電腦枱隔離影足幾日"},{"pid":"344dacc80e41eef3b0ff0a